snippet.title: Ghost Official Trailer | Dr.Shivarajkumar, Anupam Kher, Jayaram, Prashant Narayanan | Sandesh |Srini
snippet.description:
This action packed heist thriller, directed by Srini, tells the story of one man's quest for justice. This apart, the film offers a link to the second installment of "Birbal Trilogy", the director's most awaited legal thriller. Powerhouse talents such as Dr Shivarajkumar, Anupam Kher, Jayaram, Prashanth Narayanan, Archana Jois, Satyaprakash and Dattanna are part of the film's main cast.
Arjun Janya's striking background scores and cinematographer Mahendra Simha's captivating visuals promise to take the film a notch higher.
We now welcome you to the world of #GHOST. See you in the cinemas this Dasara.(October 2023)

Mastering Studio : Beracha Studios ( Chennai )

snippet.title: Tejas Official Teaser | Kangana Ranaut | Sarvesh M | Ronnie S | In Cinemas 27 Oct
snippet.description:
She is ready to take off, for the love of her nation kyunki agar Bharat ko chhedoge toh chhodenge nahi! 

Trailer out on Indian Air Force Day, 8th October. 

#TejasTeaser 
#BharatKoChhedogeTohChhodengeNahi 
#Tejas In cinemas on 27th Oct.

Tejas is the story of the courageous female IAF officer - Tejas Gill, who’s determined to safeguard the nation at all costs. It’s India’s first air action film which also showcases India’s first indigenous fighter jet - Tejas.
With the motto of ‘Bharat Ko Chhedoge, Toh Chhodenge Nahi’, the makers of Uri are set to bring another ultimate patriotic film! 

Written and Directed By Sarvesh Mewara 
Produced By Ronnie Screwvala

Song 
Apni Jeet Karoon 
Music Composed By - Shashwat Sachdev
Singers - Simran Choudhary and Shashwat Sachdev

snippet.title: HONEY CANDY | Thaen Mittai | 90's Kids Special Snacks | Dessert Candy Recipe Cooking in Village
snippet.description:
Thaen Mittai is one of the popular 90's kids' favorite snack candies from childhood. Today, we make Honey Candy using Red Dragon fruit extract instead of artificial food color. We use rock sold for sugar syrup. After a day of cooking, we enjoy our favorite Thaen Mittai!

Tasty!

snippet.description:
#CID #सीआईडी #cid2023 

Click here to subscribe to SONY WAH: https://www.youtube.com/@SonyWAH

A music launch is going to take place of a film. An actress gives an interview when a body falls from the sky onto her car. The investigation reveals that the body is of the hero Kunal. Can CID solve the case of the hero?

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #सीआईडी #CID2023 #CrimeThrillers #CrimeMysteries #Mysteries #Horror #NewCID #Crime #NewCID #LatestCID #sonywah 
      
About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.
        
Click here to watch more episodes of CID: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL1Vjcsuog4C5XmPDaj5iWn1Adytfd-goP

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War," was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. The recent release Pathaan (2023) starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham is the fourth instalment in the spy universe franchise.

All the films of the Spy Universe are blockbusters with Pathaan being the all-time highest grossing Hindi film ever. The YRF Spy Universe is now one of the biggest IP’s in the history of Indian cinema. The next film from this franchise is Tiger 3 releasing this Diwali!

YRF Spy Universe films boast of incredible visual spectacles with high-octane action sequences, thrilling plot-lines, power-packed characters and musical chartbusters.

snippet.title: Power Star PAWAN SINGH - Tujhe Na Dekhu Toh Chain | Akanksha Puri | Kalpana Patwari | Bhojpuri Song
snippet.description:
इंतजार की घड़ी हुई ख़तम! Pawan Singh और Akanksha Puri के साथ धमाल मचाएंगे "Tujhe Na Dekhu Toh Chain" के इस सुपरहिट गाने में, जिसे Pawan Singh और Kalpana Patwari ने गाया है।🔥

इस नए भोजपुरी गान का मज़ा लेते रहिये और हमारे चैनल को सब्सक्राइब करके टिप्स भोजपुरी के साथ जुड़े रहिये.

Lyrics:
मुखड़ा
F- छुप-छुप के काहे तु निहारेलs
नज़री से बान हमके मारेलs
M - तोहरा से दूर होके जियल जाता नहीं
तुझे न देखु तो चैन मुझे आता नहीं
एक तेरे सिवा कोई और मुझे भाता नहीं

अंतरा 1:
M - याद में तू,ख्वाब में तु,सांस में तु,हमरा हर एहसास में तु
F - ऐसे न मीठी मीठी बोलिया से गोलिया दागल करा
बन के चकोरा हमरा पीछे पीछे बाबु जनी लागल करा
M - दिल के हाल का बा अब कहाता नहीं
तुझे न देखु तो चैन मुझे आता नहीं
एक तेरे सिवा कोई और मुझे भाता नहीं

अंतरा 2:
M - खाके कसम कहिले हम तोहरा बिना
दूर अब रौशन पवन रही ना
F - कैसे विस्वास तोहपे करी हो डर लागेला
हमरी उमर लड़िकैया हो मन भागेला
M - प्यार में केहू ऐसे तड़पाता नहीं
तुझे न देखु तो चैन मुझे आता नहीं
एक तेरे सिवा कोई और मुझे भाता नहीं

snippet.title: बिना तली मूंग पकौड़ी की सब्जी - तेल कम खाना हैं तो इसे बनायें - No-Fry Moong Dal Pakodi Curry Recipe
snippet.description:
मूंगदाल पकौडी की सब्जी, बस जरा से तेल में बनी लेकिन बेहद स्वादिष्ट, Healthy Moong Pakodi Ki Sabji, Low-Oil Moong Pakodi Curry, No-Fry Moong Pakoda Curry,  Low-Calorie Moong Pakodi Ki Sabji, 

#moongdal #sabji #curry #pakodi 

Ingredients for
Non Fried Moong Dal Pakoda Sabzi
धुली मूंगदाल - Moong dhuli dal - 1/2 cup (100 gms)
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1 no
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 inch
हींग - Asafoetida - 1 pinch
नमक - Salt - 1/4 tsp
हरा धनिया - Coriander - 1-2 tsp
तेल - Oil - 2 tbsp
तेज पत्ता - Bay leaf - 1 no
काली मिर्च - Black pepper - 6 no
लौंग - Cloves - 3 no
बडी इलाइची - Black cardamom - 1 no, crushed
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1/2 tsp
टमाटर - Tomato - 2 no
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1 no
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 inch
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1 tsp
हींग - Asafoetida - 1 pinch
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/3 tsp
कश्मीरी लाल मिर्च - Kashmiri red chilli - 3/4 tsp
दही - Curd - 1/2 cup
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
हरा धनिया - Coriander

snippet.title: Hijacking of Singapore Airline Flight SQ 117|ത്രില്ലർ|BS Chandra Mohan| Mlife Daily
snippet.description:
Hijacking of Singapore Airline Flight SQ 117

The plane, an Airbus A310 with registration 9V-STP, had taken off from Sultan Abdul Aziz Shah Airport in Subang near Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia at 21:15 SST, with 114 passengers and 11 crew on board.[3] The plane was hijacked in mid-air while en route to Singapore Changi Airport by four Pakistanis. The hijackers were armed with explosives and knives but no firearms.

 It landed safely at Changi Airport at 22:15, where a group of officials from the Ministry of Defence, Ministry of Home Affairs and Ministry of Information, Communications and the Arts, along with Singapore Airlines representatives and a negotiating team, were waiting.

The hijackers, who claimed to be members of the Pakistan Peoples Party (PPP), demanded the release of former Prime Minister of Pakistan Benazir Bhutto's husband, Asif Ali Zardari (later elected President of Pakistan), as well as other PPP members from jail. The hijackers also required the plane to be refuelled to fly to Australia.[citation needed] The next morning, 27 March, at 02:30, the hijackers pushed two (male) flight attendants, flight steward Bernard Tan and chief steward Philip Cheong, out of the aircraft, after the plane had been moved to the outer tarmac.[citation needed]

At 06:45, the hijackers gave a last 5-minute deadline, and issued a threat to kill one passenger every ten minutes if their demands were still not met. With three minutes to go, orders were given to initiate the assault: the Singapore Armed Forces Commando Formation (SAF CDO FN) stormed the plane in a 30-second sweep, killing all four hijackers with no injuries to hostages. The hijack leader had been shot five times in the chest, but was still alive. He then attempted to stand and ignite his explosive but a commando shot him dead before he did so. The plane was completely secured by 06:50

snippet.title: Aami Shei Manushta Aar Nei(আমি সেই মানুষটা আর নেই)| Dawshom Awbotaar |Anupam|Srijit|Jio Studios|SVF
snippet.description:
আমরা সবাই যে মানুষটা ছিলাম কোনও একসময়, যে মানুষটা হতে চেয়েছিলাম একদিন, ধাক্কা খেতে খেতে সেই মানুষটা কোথায় হারিয়ে যায়! সেই বদলে যাওয়া, হেরে যাওয়া মানুষদের গল্প বলে "আমি সেই মানুষটা আর নেই"। অনুপম রায়-এর কথা-সুরে ও তারই কন্ঠে সৃজিত মুখার্জির সিনেমা "দশম অবতার" - এর গান আমি সেই মানুষটা আর নেই শুনে নিন exclusively SVF এ।

We all were once that person we aspired to become someday, but as life's blows keep coming, that person gets lost along the way. The stories of those who've changed, who've been lost and transformed, are told in the song, "Aami Shei Manushta Aar Nei." Written, composed, and sung by Anupam Roy, this song is from Srijit Mukherji's most awaiting film, "Dawshom Awbotaar." Listen exclusively on SVF.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony SAB Channel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Roshan, Taarak, and Iyer went to the Abdul Soda shop, and there Abdul welcomed everybody with a pure heart and said some lines in Urdu, which Iyer couldn't get. Now stay tuned to see how Abdul explains Iyer Urdu.

Show Name: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah 
Star Cast: Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt 
Episode No: 2934
Produced By: Asit Kumar Modi 

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #sab #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble for all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son, he calls his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal. 

Click here to watch more episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7YIF3c4EEilN5qb7tXxl2dx

snippet.title: 03 October 2023 | The Hindu Newspaper Analysis | UPSC Current Affairs Live | Drishti IAS
snippet.description:
Today’s News PDF Telegram Link: https://t.me/newsanalysisdrishtiias
InNews Programme PDF: https://t.me/innewsdrishtiias

03 October  2023 | Hindu Newspaper Analysis | UPSC Current Affairs Live | Drishti IAS

Welcome to our latest Hindu Newspaper Analysis discussion programme on the most pertinent news and current events from The Hindu News Paper, as they pertain to the UPSC Civil Services Exam (CSE). As a student preparing for the CSE, it is imperative to stay informed and up to date on the latest happenings in the country. In this video, Akshay Shukla will provide a thorough and analytical examination of the news, delving into its relevance and potential impact on the CSE. Join us as we navigate through the current events, giving you a competitive edge in your preparation for the CSE.
=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵=̵
NCERT कोर्स में नामांकन के लिये इस लिंक पर क्लिक करें : 
https://www.drishtiias.com/hindi/online-pendrive-courses/ncert-courses

NTA/ UGC-NET पेपर-1 कोर्स में नामांकन के लिये इस लिंक पर क्लिक करें : 
https://www.drishtiias.com/hindi/online-pendrive-courses/nta-ugc-net-paper-1

03 October  2023 | Hindu Newspaper Analysis | UPSC Current Affairs Live | Drishti IAS

Welcome to our latest Hindu Newspaper Analysis discussion programme on the most pertinent news and current events from The Hindu News Paper, as they pertain to the UPSC Civil Services Exam (CSE). As a student preparing for the CSE, it is imperative to stay informed and up to date on the latest happenings in the country. In this video, Akshay Shukla will provide a thorough and analytical examination of the news, delving into its relevance and potential impact on the CSE. Join us as we navigate through the current events, giving you a competitive edge in your preparation for the CSE.

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2 | Flowers | EP# 352
snippet.description:
സ്വാമിയെ കാണാൻ ആശ്രമത്തിലേക്ക് പോകാൻ തീരുമാനിച്ച് നീലു. നീലുവിന്റെ നീക്കം തടയാൻ ഉറപ്പിച്ച് ബാലു. നീലുവിനെ തടയാൻ ബാലുവിന് സാധിക്കുമോ?

"Neelu decided to go to the ashram to see Swami. Balu is determined to stop Neelu's move. Will Balu be able to stop Neelu? Let's see what will happen in 'Uppum Mulakum'!"

snippet.description:

Episode 3891: Bhagwan Ke Abhushan Ki Raksha
--------------------------------------------------------
After Sonu's performance, everyone is excited about the upcoming performances. Tapu Sena declares that this year Babita and Anjali are going to present a special act which makes everyone excited. Later that night, Bhide gets worried about guarding the Ganapati Idol because of Danger Bhai's gold chain and special modak. Sodhi, Abdul, and Tapu Sena take the responsibility to stay awake to keep an eye on the Mandap. Bhide tells Madhavi that his trepidation levels are soaring high. Madhavi tells Bhide to have faith in Tapu Sena. later, A couple with a kid tries to trespass Gokuldham. Stay tuned to learn more! 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3891, 2 Oct 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: MC SQUARE | Mashooka - Official Music Video
snippet.description:
Watch the official music video of Mashooka by MC SQUARE.

Audio Credits : 
Lyrics and Performed by: MC SQUARE
Ragini lyrics by: Aazad Singh
Music: Hiten

Video credits : 
Directed and Edited by : INFLICT
Project head and Artist managed by: Himanshu Bhatt
DOP : Vishal Anand
Female Lead : Gungun Bakshi
Assistant Director : Sarthak Gorla
Assistant DOP : Luv Gandhi 
Production Head : Akshat Bhargava
Art Director: Karma arts
Gaffer : Lokendra Singh  
Production Accountant : CA Mayank Kumar 
Executive Producer : Anant Sharma
Camera : Java motion pictures
Lights : Inder lights 
Jimmy Jib : Manish
Casting : Amandeep Singh
Stylist : Akshita Chaudhary 
Styling Assistant : Udita Mangla
Choreographer : Nancy Dogra
Laser Designer : Manpreet Singh (Laserspacee)
Laser Assistant : Vidhyaanad
Casting: Raj Kaali
MUA : Monu
DI Colorist : Onkar Singh 
Vanity & Genset : Bobby
Spot : Pradeep and team

Production House : BLVCKHOLE MEDIA

Kadka dekhu baat hilaave haath chubaare aadi,
Neeche aake karle ne do baat chubaare aadi,
Tu bethi chubaare pe ger khaat baal sukhaane,
Me khada gaad teri ke me mere paav dukhaake,
Tu kadi taakti bhi konya tera naam pukaare,
Isi bijdi si padi, mera kaadja kaanpe,
Kaadi thar mere tade 1 seat khaali laado,
Pooche baap boldio karu geetkaari laado,
Main Nyu e kona pau meri fees bhaari laado,
Mere aage paache kaade suit 30, 40 laado,
Par tere karke re saare kaam chhod rakhe,
Dhara lath seat tade saare beri god rakhe,
Haryana ke chhore ne record tod rakhe,
Bhola bhagat me tere saami haath jod rakhe,
Teri soch me pada su mere din raat ek,
Baat aage kaise badhe chhori bin baat ke,
Me roj nyu hi haandu teri sheher ke me chhori,
Meri aangdi te bahar Din gin baat ke,
Tere ishaq me isa fasa mere chain pade din raat nahi,
Supne me dikhe ja s, sodhi ke me gaat nahi
Tu jimein saavan, kaadja yo dharti mera,
Tere taayi chhora gujjar ka narmi lera,
Ek aud bhole baba ke darshan hove,
Meri chhaat te dikhe se laado ghar bhi tera,
Meri saami aake sharam tu kariye na,
Rahve aankh laal par kadi dariye na,
Gel ghumne chalaange chhar dhaam chhori,
2 baat kadi kar par kadi ladiye na,
Khair Kabhi baat kiya kar,
Mujhe Ilzaam de, fir mujhe maaf kiya kar,
Kabhi palke jhuka, shaam ko raat kiya kar,
Tahle sapno me jab, mujhe saath kiya kar,
Mashooka ki marji chaale, aashiq ke kuch haath nahi,
Me te pagal hoya firu tu karti kade baat nahi,

#mashooka #mcsquare #hiphop #desihiphop #haryanvimusic #haryanvi #haryanatoglobe #rap #desirap #haryanvirap
Audio on Sony Music Entertainment India Pvt. Ltd (C) 2023

snippet.title: Music Industry, Income, MS Dhoni, SRK & More ft. @harrdysandhu  | FO 128 - Raj Shamani
snippet.description:
Order 'Build, Don't Talk' (in English) here: https://amzn.eu/d/eCfijRu
Order 'Build Don't Talk' (in Hindi) here: https://amzn.eu/d/4wZISO0

--------------

Subscribe To Our Other YouTube Channels:-

https://www.youtube.com/@rajshamaniclips

https://www.youtube.com/@RajShamani.Shorts

---------------

In this episode of Figuring Out podcast, Raj Shamani talks with the multi-talented Harrdy Sandhu, renowned Indian singer and actor. Together, they explore Harrdy's inspiring journey through music, cricket, and the challenges he overcame on his path to stardom. The conversation begins with a glimpse into Harrdy's early ambitions, where he reflects on his dream of becoming a musician and his background in cricket. He shares anecdotes about cricket legends like MS Dhoni. Harrdy's journey from the cricket field to the music stage is nothing short of remarkable.

Raj delves into Harrdy's decision to transition from cricket to music, a pivotal moment in his life. He opens up about his journey, setbacks, and the relentless determination that eventually propelled him into the world of music. Raj and Harrdy touch on various aspects of the music industry, from the creative process behind building a song to the economics of music. Harrdy shares insights into how artists earn through streaming platforms, live shows, brand collaborations, and royalties. He also discusses his experiences working with other artists, like Sidhu Moose Wala, and the key factors that make a song successful.

The episode concludes with a thought-provoking discussion about the portrayal of struggle stories in Indian music. Harrdy challenges the notion that struggle is a prerequisite for success in the music industry, emphasizing the importance of talent, dedication, and a strong fan base. Join Raj Shamani and Harrdy Sandhu in this illuminating podcast episode, where they shed light on the dynamics of the music industry. Make sure you watch this episode till the end!

-------------

snippet.title: Composing for Jawan | Inside Anirudh Ravichander’s Studio | Anupama Chopra | Film Companion
snippet.description:
Anirudh Ravichander dissects his musical journey with Anupama Chopra, with a tour of his incredible garage studio. From his debut sensation "Why This Kolaveri Di", to orchestrating scores for blockbuster films like Jawan, Jailer, Vikram & Leo - the composer takes us through his collaborations with eminent directors like Atlee, Lokesh Kanagaraj, Nelson. He also tells us about the process of creating for superstars like Rajinikanth, Kamal Haasan and Shah Rukh Khan.

#jawan #jailer #anirudh

The Film Companion is a web channel intended to promote Indian cinema through films review, interviews, discussions, video essays, and analytical compilations. It is intended primarily for the purpose of encouraging informed discussions, criticism, and review of cinema and towards such purpose, the programs use short extracts of cinematograph films, sound recording, and photographic works. These clips and extracts are of a minimal nature and the use is not intended to interfere in any manner with their commercial exploitation of the complete work by the owners of the copyright. en-IN.title: Composing for Jawan | Inside Anirudh Ravichander’s Studio | Anupama Chopra | Film Companion
en-IN.description:
Anirudh Ravichander dissects his musical journey with Anupama Chopra, with a tour of his incredible garage studio. From his debut sensation "Why This Kolaveri Di", to orchestrating scores for blockbuster films like Jawan, Jailer, Vikram & Leo - the composer takes us through his collaborations with eminent directors like Atlee, Lokesh Kanagaraj, Nelson. He also tells us about the process of creating for superstars like Rajinikanth, Kamal Haasan and Shah Rukh Khan.

snippet.description:
दिल थाम के बैठल रहs...#Neelkamal भईया आगए है दिलो की धड़कने बढ़ाने अपने नए गाने पगली देखावे अगरबत्ती पs🔥 

नीलकमल भईया के सभी सुपरहिट गाने - https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLmZzEd9Tg_lXgTQ6reFHNrnIS-kjme8VT

Credits:
Song name - Pagli Dekhave Agarbatti
Singer - Neelkamal Singh 
Feat - Neelkamal Singh And Raksha Gupta 
Writter - Ashutosh Tiwari 
Music - Shubham Raj (SBR)
Director & Choreographer Lakkie Vishwakarma 
DOP - Yogesh Singh 
Editor - LLV Lab ( Lavkesh Vishwakarma)
D.I Rohit Singh

Original Credits:
Original Album : Hum Aapke Hain Koun
Original Singer : Lata Mangeshkar,S.P. Balasubrahmanyam
Original Lyricist : Dev Kohli
Original Music Director : Raamlaxman

Lyrics:
लागता क दिही दीवाना हो - 2
फोटो के चूमे ले रोजाना हो  - 2

मान लेले बिया हमके पति,पगली देखावे अगरबती..
बनल चाह तिया श्रीमती,पगली देखावे अगरबती

रह तिया जागल, भइल बिया पागल,उ मानेले हमरा के देवता हो
कइल चाहे शादी,बाजा बाजवा दी,छपा लेले बिया उ नेवता हो
पूजा करे लेके धूप बती,पगली देखावे अगरबती
बनल चाह तिया श्रीमती,पगली देखावे अगरबती....

उ सजे सँवरे,त आ जाले घरे,पीछे पीछे आशु उ चलके हो
बा चेहरा नूरानी, ई परियन के रानी,दीवानी भइल नीलकमल के हो
दूर ना रहेले एको रति,पगली देखावे अगरबती
मान लेले बिया हमके पति,पगली देखावे अगरबती..

snippet.title: Kalank Episode 40 - [Eng Sub]  Hira Mani - Junaid Khan - Nazish Jahangir - Sami Khan - 2nd Oct 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kalank Episode 40 - [Eng Sub]  Hira Mani - Junaid Khan - Nazish Jahangir - Sami Khan - 2nd October 2023

"Kalank" follows Sara, a determined MBA graduate seeking a job while living with her parents. Her aunt perceives Sara as a threat to her daughter's wedding prospects, adding tension to their household. Meanwhile, Sara and her cousin Wahaj develop feelings for each other, leading to potential marriage plans.
However, Sara's faces a set of unfortunate events when she joins a new office and encounters Sarfaraz, a manager with malicious intent. He defames and disrespects her, triggering a series of troubles and crises in her professional and personal life.
As false accusations tarnish her reputation, Sara faces an uphill battle to prove her innocence. The drama intensifies as doubts and skepticism surround her. Will she be able to restore her credibility and regain her standing in society? Amidst the chaos, the future of Sara and Wahaj's relationship hangs in the balance. Will their love survive the challenges posed by external forces and family pressure?

Written by: Edison Idrees Masih
Directed by: Mohsin Mirza
Produced by: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast: 
Hira Mani - Sara
Junaid Khan - Wahaj

Nazleen Nasar - Hameeda

snippet.title: 21 Days Challenge Reprogram YOUR MIND for SUCCESS! What to say when you talk to yourself ! SeeKen
snippet.description:
What to say when you talk to yourself Book summary in Hindi ! Self Talk Affirmation ! Positive Affirmations ! Self talk Motivation

What to say when you talk to yourself Book Summary in Hindi | Self Talk Affirmations
| Positive Affirmations | Self Talk Motivation
In this video, Zeeshan delves into the life-changing book "What to Say When You Talk
to Yourself" by Shad Helmstatter. This self-help masterpiece explores the incredible
impact of positive self-talk, positive affirmations, and effective self-management
techniques on our lives. Discover the art of changing brain programming through the
magic of affirmations.

Helmstatter's book is a secret treasure of insights into harnessing the power of your
subconscious mind to reshape your beliefs and behaviours, ultimately boosting your
confidence and motivation for success. This book summary in Hindi offers a concise
yet comprehensive guide to reprogram your brain and achieve the personal and
professional success you've always desired.
Unlock the secrets of positive self-talk, affirmations, self-management, and the
transformative impact they can have on your life.

snippet.title: World’s Smallest Nerf Gun Shoots an Ant
snippet.description:
Creating the World’s smallest Nerf gun 5 times in a row. Reserve your CrunchLabs Build Box for the holidays here- https://crunchlabs.com

I started a company called CrunchLabs, where we build a toy together, and then I teach you all the juicy physics for how it works. So if you want to learn to think like an engineer and have a really fun time doing it, check out the current promotion where you get 2 FREE boxes at https://crunchlabs.com

Thanks to these folks for providing some of the music in the video: 
A Shell in the Pit - https://ashellinthepit.bandcamp.com/
Ponder - @pondermusic   
Laura Shigihara - @supershigi 
Andrew Applepie - https://soundcloud.com/andrewapplepie 
Blue Wednesday - https://soundcloud.com/bluewednesday 

Special thanks to my friends at BYU - Larry Howell, Brian Jensen, Spencer Magleby, Terri Bateman, Felipe Rivera, Jacob Sheffield, Grant Ogilvie, Bridget Kember, Bethany Parkinson, Aliya Bascom, James Wade, Hunter Pruett, Jared Hunter, Luke Gardner, Ivyann Running, Michael Linder, Brooklyn Peters, Jared Erickson, Austin Martel, Kyle Dahl, Julie Walker, Adam Sanders, Matt Michell and Barret Schoenrock.

Download files for compliant mechanisms that you can 3D print (including a compliant mechanism blaster): https://compliantmechanisms.byu.edu/maker-resources
 
To learn more about the BYU Compliant Mechanisms Research Group (CMR), see https://compliantmechanisms.byu.edu/

Also, thanks to the very talented group of researchers from the Salk Institute, UC San Diego, and UC San Francisco: Lauren P. Takiguchi, Jocelyn G. Olvera, Amanda L. Wacker, Ryan J. Fantasia, Boyu Liu, and Pallav Kosuri, Wade Shipley of UC San Diego, and Konlin Shen, Roopal Rawani, Amy Cao, Mike Jeffs, and Victoria Johnson.

To read more about DNA Origami NanoNERF Blasters, please visit https://kosurilab.com/docs/Takiguchi-Rober-Kosuri-nanoNERF-manuscript

To learn more about Pallav Kosuri’s research and to support him in making DNA machines that improve human health, please visit https://www.salk.edu/kosuri. To support his work, click on the ‘give’ button and note ‘Kosuri Lab’ in the comments. 

 
NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. Promotion starts on 1/1/2023 & ends on 12/31/23, subject to monthly entry deadlines. Open to legal residents of the 50 U.S. & D.C., 18+. 1 prize per month: each month is its own separate promotion. For the first 2-3 months, winner may be notified via phone call instead of winning game piece. If a monthly prize is unclaimed/forfeited, it will be awarded via 2nd chance drawing. See Official Rules at crunchlabs.com/sweepstakes for full details on eligibility requirements, how to enter, free method of entry, prize claim procedure, prize description and limitations. Void where prohibited.

vi.title: Chế Tạo Khẩu Súng Nerf Nhỏ Nhất Thế Giới Bắn Được Kiến
vi.description:
4 lần lập kỷ lục với loạt khẩu súng Nerf nhỏ nhất Thế Giới chưa từng được làm ra.

Tôi đã bắt đầu thành lập công ty CrunchLabs để nghiên cứu và chế tạo ra nhiều loại đồ chơi chất lừ. Chưa dừng lại ở đó, sứ mệnh của CrunchLabs chính là truyền thụ những kiến thức vật lý vô cùng thú vị đằng sau cách thức hoạt động của từng món đồ chơi. Nếu bạn muốn học cách tư duy như một kỹ sư đích thực và tận hưởng khoảng thời gian mày mò vừa vui vừa bổ ích, hãy khám phá ngay ưu đãi hiện có để nhận 2 hộp lắp ráp MIỄN PHÍ tại https://crunchlabs.com

Xin chân thành gửi lời cảm ơn đến các tác giả của phần âm nhạc xuất sắc trong video: 
A Shell in the Pit - https://ashellinthepit.bandcamp.com/
Ponder - @pondermusic   
Laura Shigihara - @supershigi 
Andrew Applepie - https://soundcloud.com/andrewapplepie 
Blue Wednesday - https://soundcloud.com/bluewednesday 

Xin đặc biệt cảm ơn đến những người bạn đáng mến của tôi tại BYU - Larry Howell, Brian Jensen, Spencer Magleby, Terri Bateman, Felipe Rivera, Jacob Sheffield, Grant Ogilvie, Bridget Kember, Bethany Parkinson, Aliya Bascom, James Wade, Hunter Pruett, Jared Hunter, Luke Gardner, Ivyann Running, Michael Linder, Brooklyn Peters, Jared Erickson, Austin Martel, Kyle Dahl, Julie Walker, Adam Sanders, Matt Michell và Barret Schoenrock.

Bạn có thể tải xuống các tập tin cơ chế compliant để tiến hành in 3D tại liên kết này: https://compliantmechanisms.byu.edu/maker-resources
 
Để tìm hiểu thêm về BYU Compliant Mechanisms Research Group (Nhóm Nghiên Cứu Cơ Chế Compliant của BYU) (CMR), hãy truy cập https://compliantmechanisms.byu.edu/

Ngoài ra, xin chân thành cảm ơn đến đội ngũ những nhà nghiên cứu vô cùng tài năng đến từ Salk Institute, UC San Diego và UC San Francisco: Lauren P. Takiguchi, Jocelyn G. Olvera, Amanda L. Wacker, Ryan J. Fantasia, Boyu Liu, và Pallav Kosuri, Wade Shipley thuộc UC San Diego và Konlin Shen, Roopal Rawani, Amy Cao, Mike Jeffs cũng như Victoria Johnson. Lauren P. Takiguchi.

Để tìm hiểu thêm về nghiên cứu của Pallav Kosuri và hỗ trợ anh tạo ra các cỗ máy DNA giúp cải thiện sức khỏe cho nhân loại, bạn có thể truy cập https://www.salk.edu/kosuri. Để ủng hộ công trình nghiên của của anh ấy, hãy nhấp vào nút ‘give’ và để lại lời nhắn cho ‘Kosuri Lab’ trong phần bình luận.

th.title: ยิงปืนเนิร์ฟที่เล็กที่สุดในโลกใส่มด
th.description:
เราสร้างปืนเนิร์ฟ ที่เล็กที่สุดในโลก 5 ครั้ง

ผมก่อตั้งบริษัทชื่อ CrunchLabs ซึ่งพวกเราสร้างของเล่นด้วยกัน จากนั้นผมก็จะสอนฟิสิกส์ทั้งหมดเกี่ยวกับวิธีการทำงานของสิ่งที่สร้างขึ้น ดังนั้นหากคุณต้องการเรียนรู้ที่จะคิดแบบวิศวกร และสนุกไปกับมัน ลองดูโปรโมชั่นตอนนี้ ที่คุณจะได้รับกล่องฟรี 2 กล่องที่ https://crunchlabs.com

ขอบคุณคนเหล่านี้ที่ให้พวกเราใช้เพลงบางส่วนในวิดีโอ:
A Shell in the Pit - https://ashellinthepit.bandcamp.com/
Ponder - @pondermusic   
Laura Shigihara - @supershigi 
Andrew Applepie - https://soundcloud.com/andrewapplepie 
Blue Wednesday - https://soundcloud.com/bluewednesday 

ขอขอบคุณเป็นพิเศษสำหรับเพื่อนของผมที่ BYU - แลร์รี ฮาวเวลล์, ไบรอัน เจนเซ่น, สเปนเซอร์ แม็กเกิลบี, เทอร์รี เบทแมน, เฟลิเป้ ริเวรา, เจค็อบ เชฟฟิลด์, แกรนท์ โอกิลวี, บริดเจ็ท เคมเบอร์, เบธานี พาร์กินสัน, อลิยา บาสคอม, เจมส์ เวด, ฮันเตอร์ พรูเอตต์, จาเร็ด ฮันเตอร์, ลุค การ์ดเนอร์, ไอวีแอนน์ รันนิ่ง, ไมเคิล ลินเดอร์, บรูคลิน ปีเตอร์ส , จาเร็ด เอริกสัน, ออสติน มาร์เทล, ไคล์ ดาห์ล, จูลี วอล์กเกอร์, อดัม แซนเดอร์ส, แมตต์ มิเชล และบาร์เร็ต เชินร็อค

ดาวน์โหลดไฟล์สำหรับกลไกต่างๆที่คุณสามารถพิมพ์แบบ 3 มิติได้ (รวมถึงกลไกบลาสเตอร์): https://Complimentmechanisms.byu.edu/maker-resources
 
หากต้องการเรียนรู้เพิ่มเติมเกี่ยวกับกลุ่มวิจัยกลไกของ BYU (CMR) โปรดดู https://Compliantmechanisms.byu.edu/

นอกจากนี้ ขอขอบคุณกลุ่มนักวิจัยที่มีความสามารถมากจาก สถาบันซอล์ค, UC San Diego และ UC San Francisco: ลอเรน พี. ทาคิกูจิ, โจเซลิน จี. โอลเวรา, อแมนดา แอล. แวคเกอร์, ไรอัน เจ. แฟนตาเซีย, ป๋อหยู หลิว และ ปัลลาฟ โคซูรี, เวด ชิปลีย์ จาก UC ซานดิเอโก และ คอนลิน เสิน,รูปาล ราวานี, เอมี่ เฉา, ไมค์ เจฟส์, วิคตอเรีย จอห์นสัน และ ลอเรน พี. ทากิกุจิ.

หากต้องการอ่านเพิ่มเติมเกี่ยวกับ ดีเอ็นเอโอริกามิ นาโนเนิร์ฟ บลาสเตอร์ (DNA Origami NanoNERF Blasters) โปรดไปที่ https://kosurilab.com/docs/Takiguchi-Rober-Kosuri-nanoNERF-manuscript

หากต้องการเรียนรู้เพิ่มเติมเกี่ยวกับการวิจัยของ Pallav Kosuri และสนับสนุนเขาในการสร้างเครื่อง ดีเอ็นเอ เพื่อพัฒนาสุขภาพมนุษย์ โปรดไปที่ https://www.salk.edu/kosuri เพื่อสนับสนุนงานของเขา คลิกที่ปุ่ม “บริจาค” และเขียน "Kosuri Lab" ไว้ในคอมเม้นต์ด้วยนะครับ

ar.description:
🔫 صنعت مسدس نيرف أصغر بـ 10 الاف مرة من الحجم الطبيعي!

🔧 أنشأت شركة تدعى CrunchLabs حيث نبني لعبة مثيرة معًا ثم أعلمك كل الفيزياء حول طريقة عملها، لذلك إذا كنت تريد أن تتعلم كيف تفكر كمهندس وتستمتع حقًا بوقتك في القيام بذلك، تحقق من العرض الترويجي على الموقع لتحصل على صندوقين مجانيين https://crunchlabs.com

🎶 شكرًا لهؤلاء الأشخاص على تقديمهم بعض الموسيقى في الفيديو:
Ponder - https://youtube.com/@Pondermusic 
Laura Shigihara -  @supershigi  
Andrew Applepie - https://soundcloud.com/andrewapplepie 
Blue Wednesday - https://soundcloud.com/bluewednesday 

شكر خاص لأصدقائي في جامعة "بريغهام يونغ": لاري هاول، برايان جينسن، سبنسر ماغليبي، تيري بيتمان، فيليب ريفيرا، جاكوب شفيلد، جرانت أوغليفي، بريدجيت كيمبر، بيثاني باركينسون، عليا باسكوم، جيمس ويد، هنتر برويت، جاريد هنتر، لوك غاردنر، آيفيان رنينج، مايكل ليندر، بروكلين بيترز، جاريد إريكسون، أوستن مارتل، كايل دال، جولي ووكر، آدم ساندرز، مات ميتشيل وباريت شونروك.

إذا كنتم تقومون بالطباعة ثلاثية الأبعاد فيمكنكم تحميل الملفات الخاصة بالآليات التوافقية (بما في ذلك مكبر الآلية اتوافقية) من هنا: https://compliantmechanisms.byu.edu/maker-resources

لمعرفة المزيد عن مجموعة أبحاث الآليات التوافقية في جامعة بريغهام يونغ (BYU CMR)، قوموا بزيارة https://compliantmechanisms.byu.edu

كما نشكر مجموعة الباحثين الموهوبين جدًا من معهد سولك وجامعة كاليفورنيا سان دييغو، وجامعة كاليفورنيا سان فرانسيسكو: لورين ب. تاكيجوتشي، جوسلين جي. أولفيرا، أماندا إل. واكر، ريان ج. فانتازيا، بويو ليو، وبالاف كوسوري، وويد شيبلي من جامعة كاليفورنيا سان دييغو، وكونلين شين، روبال رواني، إيمي كاو، مايك جيفس، وفيكتوريا جونسون. لورين ب. تاكيجوتشي.

للمزيد من المعلومات حول مسدسات النيرف بتقنية الحمض النووي، يرجى زيارة https://kosurilab.com/docs/Takiguchi-Rober-Kosuri-nanoNERF-manuscript

ru.title: Самый Маленький Пистолет Nerf в Мире Стреляет в Муравья
ru.description:
Создаю самый маленький пистолет Nerf в мире 5 раз подряд. Зарезервировать CrunchLabs Билд Бокс (Build Box) к праздникам можно здесь - https://crunchlabs.com

Я основал компанию CrunchLabs, где мы вместе собираем игрушку, и затем я рассказываю вам о всех законах физики, на которых игрушка основана. Так что если ты хочешь научиться думать, как инженер и одновременно с этим весело провести время, посмотри на нынешнюю акцию, где ты получишь 2 БЕСПЛАТНЫЕ коробки на https://crunchlabs.com

Спасибо этим ребятам, что предоставили часть музыки в этом видео:
A Shell in the Pit - https://ashellinthepit.bandcamp.com/
Ponder - @pondermusic   
Laura Shigihara - @supershigi 
Andrew Applepie - https://soundcloud.com/andrewapplepie 
Blue Wednesday - https://soundcloud.com/bluewednesday

Скачать файлы для гибких механизмов, которые можно распечатать на 3D-принтере (включая бластер из гибких механизмов): https://compliantmechanisms.byu.edu/maker-resources

Более подробную информацию об исследовательской группе BYU Compliant Mechanisms Research Group (CMR) можно найти на сайте https://compliantmechanisms.byu.edu/

Кроме того, спасибо очень талантливой группе исследователей из Института Солка, Калифорнийского университета в Сан-Диего и Калифорнийского университета в Сан-Франциско: Лорен П. Такигучи, Джослин Г. Фантазии, Бою Лю и Паллаву Косури, Уэйду Шипли из Калифорнийского университета в Сан-Диего, а также Конлин Шен, Рупал Равани, Эми Као, Майку Джеффсу и Виктории Джонсон. Лорен П. Такигучи.

Более подробную информацию о ДНК оригами NanoNERF Blasters можно найти на сайте https://kosurilab.com/docs/Takiguchi-Rober-Kosuri-nanoNERF-manuscript

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. snippet.description:
Raktabeej is a taut Bengali thriller revolving around a sudden blast in a firecracker unit ahead of Durga Puja. Is there more than what meets the eye?

‘Raktabeej’ is all set to hit the big screens on 19th of October 2023.

BookMyShow Link: https://in.bookmyshow.com/kolkata/movies/raktabeej-bengali/ET00354857

উইনডোজ এবং সঞ্জয় আগরওয়াল নিবেদিত, উইনডোজ প্রযোজিত রক্তবীজ আসছে ১৯শে অক্টোবর,
বাংলা, হিন্দি, ওড়িয়া এবং অসমীয়া ভাষায়।

‘Raktabeej’ is all set to hit the big screens on 19th of October 2023.

BookMyShow Link: https://in.bookmyshow.com/kolkata/movies/raktabeej-bengali/ET00354857

উইনডোজ এবং সঞ্জয় আগরওয়াল নিবেদিত, উইনডোজ প্রযোজিত রক্তবীজ আসছে ১৯শে অক্টোবর,
বাংলা, হিন্দি, ওড়িয়া এবং অসমীয়া ভাষায়।
এবার পুজোয় পুজোর ছবি।

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Mannat Murad Episode 02 - [Eng Sub] - Iqra Aziz - Talha Chahour - Digitally Presented by PEL - 2nd October 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Mannat Murad Digitally Presented by PEL

Mannat is a beautiful young girl who hails from a progressive family that values love, care, and mutual respect. Raised in an environment where everyone's choices are respected, Mannat enjoys the freedom to make her own decisions. Following the untimely demise of her parents, she finds support from her elder brother, Nafees, who showers her with affection.

On the other hand, Murad belongs to a conservative family where his mother, the matriarch, wields significant influence over his life choices. As the only son, Murad is burdened with the responsibility of fulfilling his family's expectations. Soft-spoken and romantic by nature, Murad finds himself unable to defy his mother's authority, especially after the passing of his father.

Despite their starkly contrasting backgrounds, Mannat and Murad's hearts find solace in each other's presence, and they fall deeply in love. However, their families' interference creates misunderstandings between Mannat and Murad, testing the strength of their bond.

Will their families agree to their union? Will Mannat's family, with their open-mindedness, find common ground with Murad's conservative household? Can Mannat and Murad's love for each other withstand the motives of their families, who seek to create further misunderstandings between them?

Written by: Nadia Akhtar
Directed by: Syed Wajahat Hussain
Produced by: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

 FOR CHUTNEY

snippet.title: Desh Ka Dhoni | Episode 01| उद्देश्य
snippet.description:
With an aim to give tribute to the ace cricketer MS Dhoni, Gaurav starts his 2400+ km journey on a bicycle from Delhi to Chennai. On his way, he met with fans and collected wishes for MS Dhoni. Gaurav has no prior experience in cycling but he takes this mammoth task of riding 2400 Km. He faces a lot of hardships while riding in the peak summer months of April/May. He faces muscular cramps and dehydration and then plans to discontinue the trip creeps into his mind. Will he give up ?
#DeshKaDhoni #Epsode01

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kalank Episode 41 Teaser - 2nd October 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Kalank" follows Sara, a determined MBA graduate seeking a job while living with her parents. Her aunt perceives Sara as a threat to her daughter's wedding prospects, adding tension to their household. Meanwhile, Sara and her cousin Wahaj develop feelings for each other, leading to potential marriage plans.
However, Sara's faces a set of unfortunate events when she joins a new office and encounters Sarfaraz, a manager with malicious intent. He defames and disrespects her, triggering a series of troubles and crises in her professional and personal life.
As false accusations tarnish her reputation, Sara faces an uphill battle to prove her innocence. The drama intensifies as doubts and skepticism surround her. Will she be able to restore her credibility and regain her standing in society? Amidst the chaos, the future of Sara and Wahaj's relationship hangs in the balance. Will their love survive the challenges posed by external forces and family pressure?

snippet.title: 50 വയസ്സ് കഴിഞ്ഞാലും ഒരുമുടിപോലും നരക്കില്ല  മുടി വേരുമുതൽകറുക്കും  ഇങ്ങനെ ചെയ്താൽ/Dr Manoj Johnson
snippet.description:
50 വയസ്സ് കഴിഞ്ഞാലും ഒരുമുടിപോലും നരക്കില്ല  മുടി വേരുമുതൽകറുക്കും  ഇങ്ങനെ ചെയ്താൽ/Dr Manoj Johnson /#drshimji 

Causes of premature hair graying

The exact cause of premature hair graying is not fully understood, but it is thought to be a combination of genetic and environmental factors.

Genetics is the biggest factor in premature hair graying. If your parents or grandparents went gray early, you are more likely to do the same.

Environmental factors that may contribute to premature hair graying include:

Stress: Stress can damage hair follicles and accelerate the graying process.
Smoking: Smoking can damage DNA and hair follicles, leading to premature graying.
Medical conditions: Certain medical conditions, such as thyroid disease, vitiligo, and alopecia areata, can cause premature hair graying.
Nutritional deficiencies: Deficiencies in certain vitamins and minerals, such as vitamin B12, vitamin D, and copper, can also contribute to premature hair graying.
Care and prevention of premature hair graying

There is no guaranteed way to prevent premature hair graying, but there are some things you can do to help keep your hair looking its best:

Eat a healthy diet: Make sure to eat a balanced diet that includes plenty of fruits, vegetables, and whole grains. This will help ensure that you are getting the nutrients your hair needs to stay healthy.
Reduce stress: Stress can damage hair follicles and accelerate the graying process. Find healthy ways to manage stress, such as exercise, yoga, or meditation.
Quit smoking: Smoking can damage DNA and hair follicles, leading to premature graying. Quitting smoking is one of the best things you can do for your overall health, including your hair health.
Protect your hair from the sun: The sun's ultraviolet (UV) rays can damage hair follicles and accelerate the graying process. When you are outdoors, wear a hat or scarf to protect your hair from the sun.
Use gentle hair products: Avoid using harsh hair products that can damage hair follicles. Choose gentle shampoos and conditioners, and avoid using heat styling tools too often.
If you are concerned about premature hair graying, talk to your doctor. They can help you identify any underlying medical conditions that may be contributing to the problem. They can also recommend other treatments or lifestyle changes that may help.

🤝 Join us on this roller-coaster journey of friendship, love, and betrayal as we delve into the lives of two extraordinary friends from starkly contrasting backgrounds.

👸 Meet Tapasya, the pampered and privileged daughter of a wealthy man, and her best friend, Ichcha, who comes from a humble background as the daughter of a maid. Despite society's barriers, their unbreakable bond challenges conventions and stands the test of time.

💔 Love takes center stage when Veer, whose marriage proposal was rejected by Tapasya, finds solace in the companionship of Ichcha. But what ensues is a whirlwind of emotions as jealousy and heartbreak threaten to tear apart the inseparable duo.

💍 Witness a gripping twist when Tapasya, fueled by spite, takes a drastic step and marries Veer, setting off a chain of events that creates a complex love triangle. Veer finds himself torn between the two friends, entangled in a web of emotions.

snippet.title: OYE NEELAMMO | FULL SONG | LATEST FOLK SONG 2023 | LAVANYA | PARSHURAM NAGAM @MANAIRMUSICMOVIES
snippet.description:
OYE NEELAMMO | FULL SONG | LATEST FOLK SONG 2023 | LAVANYA | PARSHURAM NAGAM  @MANAIRMUSICMOVIES  

పాట నేపథ్యం:
*ఓ కరుడుకట్టిన రాక్షసుడు.. ఒక అమ్మాయిని.. చంపేసేటప్పుడు.. హీరోయిన్ చూస్తుంది. ఒక ఆ అమ్మాయిని చంపేద్దాం అని పగబడతాడు ఆ దుర్మార్గుడు. 
*కానీ ప్రతీసారి ఆమే భర్త.. ఆమె ప్రాణాలను కాపాడుతాడు.. 
*భార్యాభర్తలు ఇద్దరూ ఒకనాడు దీపావళి నోములకు అమ్మాయి వాళ్ళ ఇంటికి వెళ్లి..  మళ్ళీ హీరో వాళ్ళ ఇంటికి తిరిగిరాంగా.. చీకటి అవుతుంది.
*దగ్గర్లో ఉన్న గుడిసెలో తలదాచుకుంటారు.
*అర్థరాత్రి దాహం వేసి హీరో బయటకు రాగానే.. విలన్స్ వచ్చి.. గుడిసెకు నిప్పు అంటిస్తారు. భర్త ఎంతో ప్రయత్నం చేస్తాడు. కానీ మంటలు రానివ్వవూ. వెంటనే బావి దగ్గరకు పరుగెత్తుతాడు హీరో. 
*బావి నీళ్లు తీస్తున్న హీరోని... కాళ్ళల్లో కట్టెలతో కొట్టి బాయిలో పడేస్తారు. పైకి రాకుండా ఆ హీరో మీద రాళ్లు ఎత్తేస్తారు😢😢
*ఇంతలో రైతు అటుగా రావడంతో.. తాడు వేసిహీరోని కాపాడుతాడు.
*తర్వాత.. హీరో వెళ్లి అమ్మాయిని కాపాడతాడు..
*మరి ఈ పార్ట్ లో అయినా.. వీళ్ళు ఇల్లు చేసుకుంటారా?? లేదో.. త్వరలో విడుదల అయ్యే మరో భాగంలో చూడండి 
.plz Share చేయండి😊👍
✍️మీ పరశురాం నాగం. రైటర్ & డైరెక్టర్.

localized.title: OYE NEELAMMO | FULL SONG | LATEST FOLK SONG 2023 | LAVANYA | PARSHURAM NAGAM @MANAIRMUSICMOVIES
localized.description:
OYE NEELAMMO | FULL SONG | LATEST FOLK SONG 2023 | LAVANYA | PARSHURAM NAGAM  @MANAIRMUSICMOVIES  

పాట నేపథ్యం:
*ఓ కరుడుకట్టిన రాక్షసుడు.. ఒక అమ్మాయిని.. చంపేసేటప్పుడు.. హీరోయిన్ చూస్తుంది. ఒక ఆ అమ్మాయిని చంపేద్దాం అని పగబడతాడు ఆ దుర్మార్గుడు. 
*కానీ ప్రతీసారి ఆమే భర్త.. ఆమె ప్రాణాలను కాపాడుతాడు.. 
*భార్యాభర్తలు ఇద్దరూ ఒకనాడు దీపావళి నోములకు అమ్మాయి వాళ్ళ ఇంటికి వెళ్లి..  మళ్ళీ హీరో వాళ్ళ ఇంటికి తిరిగిరాంగా.. చీకటి అవుతుంది.
*దగ్గర్లో ఉన్న గుడిసెలో తలదాచుకుంటారు.
*అర్థరాత్రి దాహం వేసి హీరో బయటకు రాగానే.. విలన్స్ వచ్చి.. గుడిసెకు నిప్పు అంటిస్తారు. భర్త ఎంతో ప్రయత్నం చేస్తాడు. కానీ మంటలు రానివ్వవూ. వెంటనే బావి దగ్గరకు పరుగెత్తుతాడు హీరో. 
*బావి నీళ్లు తీస్తున్న హీరోని... కాళ్ళల్లో కట్టెలతో కొట్టి బాయిలో పడేస్తారు. పైకి రాకుండా ఆ హీరో మీద రాళ్లు ఎత్తేస్తారు😢😢
*ఇంతలో రైతు అటుగా రావడంతో.. తాడు వేసిహీరోని కాపాడుతాడు.
*తర్వాత.. హీరో వెళ్లి అమ్మాయిని కాపాడతాడు..
*మరి ఈ పార్ట్ లో అయినా.. వీళ్ళు ఇల్లు చేసుకుంటారా?? లేదో.. త్వరలో విడుదల అయ్యే మరో భాగంలో చూడండి 
.plz Share చేయండి😊👍
✍️మీ పరశురాం నాగం. రైటర్ & డైరెక్టర్.

snippet.title: Jetha ने किया Daya के साथ Prank | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 1 Oct 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

 Jethalal is getting ready to leave for his shop but Daya's mind scares him with a cat and he starts screaming. Jethalal also teaches a good lesson to Daya by troubling her in front of Bapu Ji and starts dancing. On the other side, Bhide tries to blackmail Taarak and Popatlal as they did not reveal the police station incident to Bhide. In the classroom, Tapu Sena and other kids are having fun, irritating Bhide. Why is Jethalal tensed?  

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 922
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu
